Dj Ecool real name Ebianga Inang Ikpeme has released a new track 4U featuring Peruzzi and multiple award winner Davido. This is one of many collaborations done by Davido who has featured in many songs this year. He has featured with Peruzzi, Duncan Mighty and others. Peruzzi is a DMW singer who has some songs under his belt. This year he released Tatashe, Run am and Hangover. He also featured in Aza. The new release 4U is a party jam with a decent rhythm and its lyrics is dedicated to a young lady being wooed. Listen to the track below: 